page.title: 17FOOTPATHS ALONG THE HILLS.
page.content: There are many{footpaths}along the hill.Some are along the bottom of the {hill}& some take you to the top of the hill. We have walked 5 footpaths & there are still lots more. On our walks we saw lots of plants and wildlife.Here are some things to be seen: {PLANTS:}Red Campion, Cranes Bill, Poppy, Cow Parsley, Celendines,{Wild {Orchid,}Vetches, Wild Mignonette. -------------------------------------- {BIRDS:}Skylark, Kestrel, Rooks, Crows, Blue Tits, Great Tits, Blackbird, {Lapwing,}Owls, Thrush. -------------------------------------- {TREES:}Ash, Sycamore, Beech, Oak, Hazel,Elm,{Larch,}Horse Chestnut. --------------------------------------
